text.paragraph:
In general, dose selection for the elderly patient should be cautious, usually starting at the low end of the dosing range (see 
                                    PRECAUTIONS: Geriatric Use
                                 ).

In general, dose selection and dose adjustment for the elderly patient should be cautious, usually starting at the low end of the dosing range (see 
                                    PRECAUTIONS: Geriatric Use
                                 ).
